usement%20parks%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20we%20travel.%20While%20massive%20numbers%20of%20families%20prefer%20to%20%26quot%3Brope%20drop%26quot%3B%20and%20rush%20into%20amusement%20parks%20the%20moment%20they%20open%2C%20my%20family%20relishes%20having%20parks%20nearly%20to%20ourselves%20in%20the%20hour%20or%20so%20before%20closing%2C%20usually%20with%20fireworks%20going%20off%20nearby.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWe've%20also%20gotten%20to%20experience%20more%20only-at-night%20events%2C%20such%20as%20the%20fantastic%20carnival-like%20atmosphere%20that%20takes%20over%20the%20ancient%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-trip-to-morocco-five-star-hotels-paid-with-points-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emedina%20in%20Marrakesh%20%3C%2Fa%3Eevery%20evening%2C%20or%20seeing%20the%20galaxy%20appear%20overhead%20in%20the%20night%20sky%20over%20the%20desert%20in%20Wadi%20Rum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22568b7b72-3d84-483f-a9d0-6b5e59d432ae%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20take%20my%20kids%20to%20places%20with%20complicated%20histories%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20parents%20tell%20me%20they%20would%20never%20take%20their%20children%20to%20places%20with%20difficult%2C%20complex%20histories.%20They%20think%20these%20places%2C%20which%20are%20often%20memorial%20sites%2C%20are%20too%20much%20for%20children%20to%20handle.%20While%20I%20understand%20their%20viewpoint%2C%20I%20want%20to%20get%20my%20kids%20out%20of%20their%20comfort%20zones%20when%20we%20travel.%20I%20believe%20allowing%20them%20to%20experience%20places%20dedicated%20to%20the%20victims%20of%20war%20and%20other%20atrocities%2C%20where%20these%20events%20took%20place%2C%20will%20make%20them%20more%20understanding%2C%20compassionate%20adults.%20I%20prepare%20my%20children%20by%20reading%20age-appropriate%20books%20and%20talking%20to%20them%20about%20where%20we%20are%20going%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-visi