0stake%20in%20the%20capitalist%20system%2C%20they%20will%20turn%20against%20it.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FBOKgwJ2cV0%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FBOKgwJ2cV0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Chamath%20Palihapitiya%20(%40chamath)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchamath%2Fstatus%2F1986076707196162068%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%205%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThiel%20said%20that%20young%20Americans%20had%20grown%20fed%20up%20with%20a%20system%20that%20many%20may%20have%20felt%20had%20left%20them%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3Bfrom%20the%20perspective%20of%20a%20broken%20generational%20compact%2C%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20pretty%20straightforward%20answer%20to%20me%2C%20namely%2C%20that%20when%20one%20has%20too%20much%20student%20debt%20or%20if%20housing%20is%20too%20unaffordable%2C%20then%20one%20will%20have%20negative%20capital%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%2For%20find%20it%20very%20hard%20to%20start%20accumulating%20capital%20in%20the%20form%20of%20real%20estate%3B%20and%20if%20one%20has%20no%20stake%20in%20the%20capitalist%20system%2C%20then%20one%20may%20well%20turn%20against%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Thiel%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOften%20described%20as%20a%20libertarian%2C%20Thiel%20wrote%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bwould%20be%20the%20last%20person%20to%20advocate%20for%20socialism%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it%20was%20important%20to%20understand%20why%20a%20large%20percentage%20of%20young%20Americans%20felt%20disconnected.%20Thiel%20spoke%20in%20support%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20at%20the%202016%20Republican%20National%20Convention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-thiel-spending-money-politics-again-house-republicans-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThiel%20distanced%20himself%20from%20politics%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%202022%20midterms%2C%20but%20has%20recently%20resumed%20supporting%20Republican%20causes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20his%20message%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-makeover-reason-email-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThiel%20was%20encouraging%20Facebook%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20think%20more%20about%20how%20to%20deploy%20his%20capital%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20spokesman%20for%20the%20Millennial%20generation.%26quot%3B%20Thiel%20said%20the%20social%20media%20network%20needed%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20stayed%20%26quot%3Battuned%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20rising%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20internal%20messages%20came%20to%20light%20amid%20an%20onslaught%20of%20lawsuits%20related%20to%20Meta's%20treatment%20of%20young%20users'%20mental%20health.%20Thirty-three%20states%20sued%20Meta%20in%20federal%20court%20while%20others%2C%20including%20Tennessee%20and%20the%20District%20of%20Columbia%2C%20filed%20suit%20in%20state%20court.%20Business%20Insider%20verified%20the%20authenticity%20of%20Thiel's%20message%2C%20which%20was%20posted%20by%20the%20newsletter%20Internal%20Tech%20Emails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Meta%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a919721-c7eb-4fa5-8397-d2a0149855cd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EYoung%20voters%20continue%20to%20warm%20to%20socialism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recent%20polling%20shows%20that%20a%20wide%20swath%20of%20younger%20Americans%20continue%20to%20hold%20positive%20views%20of%20socialism%2C%20even%20as%20the%20nation%20as%20a%20whole%20does%20not.%20An%20August%20Gallup%20poll%20found%20that%2049%25%20adults%2018%20to%2034%20had%20a%20positive%20view%20of%20socialism%2C%2010%20percentage%20points%20higher%20than%20adults%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20a%20straight%20line.%20It's%20hard%20to%20reconcile%20Thiel's%20thesis%20with%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20significant%20improvement%20among%20young%20voters%20in%202024%20compared%20to%20his%20two%20previous%20runs.%20Trump%20has%20routinely%20used%20the%20socialist%20label%20as%20a%20cudgel%20against%20his%20opponents%2C%20a%20trend%20he%20continued%20with%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20whom%20he%20also%20called%20a%20%26quot%3BMarxist%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20communist.%20(Harris%20was%20neither%20of%20those%20things.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AP%20Voter%20Poll%2C%20which%20is%20based%20on%20a%20survey%20of%20more%20than%2017%2C000%20voters%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20Virginia%2C%20California%2C%20and%20New%20York%20City%2C%20found%20most%20voters%20under%2030%20supported%20Democrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMamdani%20built%20a%20massive%20advantage%20with%20young%20voters%2C%20the%20survey%20found.%20He%20outperformed%20Former%20New%20York%20Gov.%20Andrew%20Cuomo%20by%2060%20percentage%20points%20among%20voters%20ages%2018%20to%2019%20and%20by%2038%20points%20among%20voters%20ages%2030%20to%2044.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAddressing%20his%20supporters%20Tuesday%20night%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fall-the-thinkers-and-activists-referenced-in-zohran-mamdanis-speech-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMamdani%20quoted%20Eugene%20V.%20Debs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%201900s%20American%20socialist%20leader%20who%20once%20ran%20for%20president%20while%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20young%2C%20despite%20my%20best%20efforts%20to%20grow%20older.%20I%20am%20Muslim.%20I%20am%20a%20democratic%20socialist.%20And%20most%20damning%20of%20all%2C%20I%20refuse%20to%20apologize%20for%20any%20of%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Mamdani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-thiel-email-socialism-zohran-mamdani-student-debt-housing-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1762423981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690bd57521c3f142ebfc2e0b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinside