C%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20management%20at%20Wharton%20who%20studies%20the%20effects%20of%20AI%20on%20work%2C%20entrepreneurship%2C%20and%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c2e0ee3d-3b0a-4491-a51f-33f27219d768%5C%22%3EEnter%20TAIA%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETS%20Imagine's%20experience%2C%20using%20data-wrangling%20AI%20technology%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsnowflake-ceo-outlines-vision-efficiency-profitability-ai-era-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESnowflake%20Intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20shows%20how%20persistent%20effort%20can%20yield%20real%20ROI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBodenski's%20main%20evidence%20is%20TAIA%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspara-stealth-ai-sales-startup-15-million-seed-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20agent%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20handles%20various%20aspects%20of%20customer%20service%20and%20data%20analysis%20for%20TS%20Imagine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20shared%20three%20specific%20TAIA%20examples%20that%20he%20says%20have%20eliminated%20the%20equivalent%20of%208.5%20full-time%20employees.%20TS%20Imagine%20employs%20about%2034%20data%20analysts%20in%20its%20data%20and%20global%20client%20service%20departments%2C%20so%20that's%20significant%20%26quot%3Bperson%20power%26quot%3B%20gain%2C%20Bodenski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225240ba05-611f-4def-be8a-415401c19ecc%5C%22%3ECustomer%20service%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-chatbots-customer-service-call-center-annoying-problems-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECustomer%20service%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20already%20a%20major%20area%20of%20impact%20for%20generative%20AI%20in%20the%20workplace%2C%20and%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20first%20places%20where%20TS%20Imagine%20realized%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20is%20constantly%20bombarded%20with%20questions%2C%20requests%2C%20and%20rants%20from%20demanding%2C%20fast-paced%20clients%2C%20including%20hedge%20funds%2C%20bankers%2C%20and%20traders.%20It%20traditionally%20hired%20employees%20to%20read%2C%20classify%2C%20and%20assign%20these%20customer-service%20tickets%20manually%E2%80%94a%20stressful%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20TAIA%20does%20this%20automatically%2C%20selecting%20which%20human%20professionals%20are%20available%20and%20best%20suited%20to%20handle%20each%20customer%20request%2C%20while%20adding%20relevant%20material%20to%20help%20resolve%20the%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20AI%20process%20takes%20about%20one%20minute%20per%20ticket%2C%20while%20the%20old%2C%20manual%20approach%20took%20about%2010%20minutes.%20This%20eliminated%20the%20equivalent%20of%20three%20full-time%20employees%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20time%2C%20effort%2C%20and%20other%20resources%20required%2C%20Bodenski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef07d5a8-864b-439e-8c19-7c6db9244717%5C%22%3E100%2C000%20emails%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETS%20Imagine%20receives%20a%20deluge%20of%20emails%20from%20numerous%20vendors%20who%20supply%20and%20update%20financial%20data%20on%20a%20regular%20basis.%20It%20gets%20roughly%20100%2C000%20of%20these%20messages%20every%20year.%20Some%20are%20incredibly%20important%2C%20while%20others%20are%20irrelevant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20previously%20tapped%20financially%20savvy%20staff%20in%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20London%2C%20New%20York%2C%20and%20Montreal%20to%20review%20every%20email%20and%20either%20discard%20it%20or%20assign%20it%20to%20the%20relevant%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20TAIA%20reads%20all%20these%20emails%20and%20automatically%20classifies%20and%20assigns%20them.%20TS%20Imagine%20gets%20the%20same%2C%20or%20better%2C%20results%20from%20this%20new%20AI%20process%20at%203%25%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20previous%20manual%20approach%2C%20Bodenski%20said.%20Part%20of%20those%20savings%20comes%20from%20the%20elimination%20of%202.5%20full-time%20employees%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20time%20an