0reassigned%20employees%20to%20more%20valuable%20tasks%2C%20such%20as%20data%20quality%2C%20testing%2C%20and%20client%20and%20vendor%20relationships%2C%20Bodenski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20invested%20thousands%20of%20hours%20in%20developing%20this%20AI%20technology.%20So%2C%20was%20it%20worth%20it%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20ROI%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B100%25%2C%26quot%3B%20Bodenski%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BThese%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworld-model-ai-explained-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elarge%20language%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20truly%20revolutionary.%20They're%20not%20solving%20things%20on%20their%20own%20%E2%80%94%20you%20have%20to%20implement%20and%20operationalize%20the%20technology%20properly%20and%20make%20it%20work%20for%20you.%20But%20I%20would%20not%20go%20back.%20Not%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Reach%20out%20to%20me%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabarr%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabarr%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fts-imagine-ai-roi-efficiency-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1762423203000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690a77480be9845f2dc5ba3a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fts-imagine-ai-roi-efficiency-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20recent%20Wharton%20study%20found%2074%25%20of%20enterprises%20are%20already%20generating%20positive%20return%20on%20investment%20