d%20Trump.%20Whether%20the%20videos%20are%20pro-Trump%20or%20anti-Trump%20depends%20on%20the%20audience.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMeta%20didn't%20quite%20buy%20my%20vibe%20about%20Vibes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20vast%20majority%20of%20Vibes%20content%20viewed%20is%20focused%20on%20lifestyle%20and%20entertainment%20topics%20like%20sci-fi%2C%20fashion%2C%20motivational%20themes%2C%20and%20pets%2C%26quot%3B%20Faith%20Eischen%2C%20a%20Meta%20spokesperson%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIn%20other%20words%2C%20while%20Business%20Insider%20may%20find%20this%20interesting%2C%20this%20content%20is%20not%20representative%20of%20the%20Vibes%20vibe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221272%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AI-Generated%20Donald%20Trump%20dances%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20to%20Meta's%20AI%20Vibes%20feed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F690b94750be9845f2dc5ca21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222383%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDonald%20Trump%20%E2%80%94%20the%20AI%20version%20%E2%80%94%20dances%20in%20an%20example%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bboomerslop%26quot%3B%20spreading%20across%20Meta%20AI's%20Vibes%20feed.%3Cp%3EScreengrab%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20I%20%3Cem%3Edo%3C%2Fem%3E%20find%20it%20interesting!%20And%20I%20don't%20disagree%20that%20it's%20not%20%3Cem%3Eall%3C%2Fem%3E%20Trump%2C%20Obama%2C%20and%20Biden%20videos.%20But%20there%20were%20enough%20to%20make%20it%20noticeable%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20compared%20to%20how%20the%20feed%20looked%20when%20it%20first%20launched.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2223f62274-3aa9-439d-836a-6e266a86af2f%5C%22%3EVibes%20has%20echoes%20of%20old%20Facebook%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20recall%20the%20mid-to-late%20aughts%2C%20when%20Facebook%20was%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20place%20where%20uncles%20yell%20at%20each%20other%20online.%26quot%3B%20The%20news%20feed%20at%20the%20time%20rewarded%20highly%20divisive%20content%20that%